headline: GEHC Inks License Agreement With Lantheus for Prostate Imaging Agent
summary: GE HealthCare strengthens its radiopharmaceutical portfolio by licensing Lantheus' PSMA PET imaging agent, PYLARIFY, for commercialization in Japan.
